title._content: West Hartlepool A-Team Champions N.Y., S.D. League Div. II 1937

description._content:
West Hartlepool A-Team, 'West Hartlepool A-Team Champions N.Y., S.D. League Div. II 1937'. Shows the cricket team at Park Drive ground, West Hartlepool. Back row from left to right: C.P. Thomlinson, A. Yorke, D.B. Knight, R. Williams, W. Sunley (Scorer). Third row from left to right: R.L. Stonehouse (Hon. Secretary), R.S. White, R. Cole, J. McCarthy, J. Middleton, J. Parker (Hon. Treasurer), A.J. Bailey, E. Telfer, W. Simpson (Captain), E.G. Roe, Esq. (President), H.R. Wormald (Vice-Captain), A. Shields, A.S. Leslie. Front row from left to right: P.M. Stubbs, G.L. Donaldson.

HAPMG : 1991.1
